  "text": "Also, the dynamical description of the particle behavior can be made in terms of a weight given to each stochastic trajectory [CITATION_1] . The weight is assigned according to the Langevin dynamics. It is important to mention that the weight becomes Gaussian due to the Gaussian character assigned to the noise,",
